title: NFL ATL: Top tight ends & Cam Newton vs. Andrew Luck
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Top tight ends & Cam Newton vs. Andrew Luck
description:
A room with some heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Chris Wesseling -- discuss which quarterback would receive the bigger contract on the open market: Cam Newton or Andrew Luck. Plus, Chris Wesseling reveals his preseason tight end rankings and the guys unveil two more players who are ready to make the leap.
